Draft Release Checklist

0) Update the gallery3 version string in core_installer.php

1) Tag the release, eg:
   $ git tag 3.0-beta-1
   $ git push --tags

2) Build the release, eg:
   php build.php 3.0-beta-1

3) Publish the release to sf.net
   rsync -avP -e ssh dist/gallery-3.0-beta-1.zip bharat@frs.sourceforge.net:uploads/

4) <insert docs about updating SF.net FRS stuff here>

5) Update sf.net, freshmeat.net stories

6) Publish gmc story


